    "# TazaKhabar Data Scraper Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook scrapes real data from HackerNews and saves it to the SQLite database.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Prerequisites:**\n",
    "- **Python 3.11+ required** (check with `python --version`)\n",
    "- Use a Jupyter kernel with Python 3.11+\n",
    "- Then run: `pip install -e .`\n",
    "\n",
    "Run cells in order to:\n",
    "1. Initialize the database and models\n",
    "2. Run the Who Is Hiring scraper\n",
    "3. Run the Top Stories scraper\n",
    "4. Run the Ask HN scraper\n",
    "5. Run the Show HN scraper\n",
    "6. Generate keyword frequencies for trends"
   ]
  },
